channel.title: Mac Won't Read .cfg Files
channel.description:
So I finally got my server to run on my Mac. But I get this error. [code]Last login: Thu Jan 30 14:14:52 on ttyp1 Welcome to Darwin! Codys-Macbook-Pro:~ User$ cd /Users/User/Desktop/Allstar-Scape\ v2/ Codys-Macbook-Pro:~/Desktop/Allstar-Scape v2 User$ java -Xmx512m server - Allstar-Scape v1 - .. Online! config\objects.cfg: file not found.
[/code]
